title: Park’s approval rating edges up after U.S. visit– 19 Oct 2015
text: Home › The Asian Pulse › Daily News › Park's approval rating edges up after U.S. visit– 19 Oct 2015 Park’s approval rating edges up after U.S. visit– 19 Oct 2015 Monday, October 19th, 2015 A poll released by polling agency Real meter showed that 48% of people approved of Park’s job performance, up 1.2 percentage points from a week earlier. Those who disapproved came to 4.7%, down 2.1 percentage points from a week earlier. The summit between Park and U.S. President Barack Obama in Washington, D.C. reaffirmed the alliance between the two countries.
